Bugatti Automobiles

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the Volkswagen AG subsidiary active from 1999-present. For Automobiles Ettore Bugatti (1909-1963), see Bugatti. For Bugatti Automobili S.p.A. (1987-1995), see Bugatti Automobili.
Coordinates: 48°31′36″N 7°29′59″E﻿ / ﻿48.52675556°N 7.499683333°E﻿ / 48.52675556; 7.499683333

